'''Yeom Dong-jin'''([[korea]]n:염동진, [[hanja]]廉東振, February 14, 1902 &ndash; 1950(?)) was a [[Korea]]n politician, independent activist and terrorist. Leader of [[Baikuisa]]([[hangul]]:백의사), of [[Korea]]n terrorist Groups. Ather name was '''Yeon Eung-Taik'''([[korea]]n:염응택, [[hanja]]廉應澤).

