The '''Lycée International [[Alexandre Dumas]]''' ({{lang-ar|ثانوية الكسندر دوما الدولية}}) is a French international school in [[Ben-Aknoun]], [[Algiers]], [[Algeria]].<ref>"[http://www.liad-alger.fr/joomla/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=81:mentions-legales&catid=2:uncategorised Mentions légales]." Lycée International Alexandre Dumas. Retrieved on 17 January 2015. "Siège social : Chemin Arezki Mouri - Ben-Aknoun - Algérie"</ref> It has two divisions: ''primaire'' (primary school) and ''collège-lycée'' (junior and senior high school).

